{"tid":1954770,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"中學生唔好再幫襯Afterschool呢間藍到發黑嘅網上補習","createTime":"2020-04-02T05:06:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-02T16:49:21.000Z","uid":122234,"like":19,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"f5a8d0354671743103f37864defe6308cdbc8c78","tid":1954770,"uid":122234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T05:06:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Afterschool紅底偷野食人血饅頭正仆街</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">罪名一：藍到發黑</span><br />\n呢間野係九龍塘紅底incubator租office，其中一個co-founder嘅阿爸係大陸做生意。下圖自己睇。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d3N1Doh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd3N1Doh.png&h=20d29f86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">罪名二：理直氣壯偷人野</span><br />\n當年呢間野嘅Ronald拎左HKU入面免費比中學生嘅DSE資源，Repackage完再呃鳩中學生要佢幾百蚊咁買，呃左中學生六位數字。如果你幾年前有睇高登嘅話應該會知呢件事。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4tKWshs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4tKWshs.png&h=287a3176&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n都未完，然後偷左幾十個人係IG打嘅學術分享唔撚落credit直接係網站出，之後比人踢爆左係抄文之後死作藉口唔肯認。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UDRqkAD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUDRqkAD.png&h=546a8f7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/04/02/014025_26df3f8e4ef0f1931b546780132a2f3e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F04%2F02%2F014025_26df3f8e4ef0f1931b546780132a2f3e.png&h=e9be4a3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">罪名三：扮黃食人血饅頭</span></span><br />\n呢條紅底撚你估唔到佢會攞運動當條橋黎做Marketing，話說佢出左個Post話「停課不停學」，想啲良心老師、學生捐一啲自己嘅筆記搞個資源庫。<br />\n<br />\n好多唔知佢底細嘅人就信左真係比左啲資源佢，點左去到之後啲資源係你一定要註冊佢個濕鳩網站先拎到，仲要一路download一路有佢其他課程嘅廣告，入左去之後一隻有關香港嘅字都無，只係話「DSE資源庫」。居心係咩我諗大家都明，之後有人踢爆左，有唔少人老師發現中伏withdraw左，但佢依家個資源庫仲係度。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ybaCbG3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FybaCbG3.png&h=9a4b2e42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CBZGDnc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCBZGDnc.png&h=bc81aeb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c92H7g0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc92H7g0.png&h=fb0a8793&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TBt8nbE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTBt8nbE.png&h=a2769d1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最後，如果見到呢個Post嘅你有買過AfterSchool嘅野，請你即時申請退款</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果你同AfterSchool有合作過，希望你唔好再同流合污，即刻終止合作並withdraw content</span></span><br />\n<br />\n麻煩各位，唔好比呢條呃中學生嘅深紅撚樣得逞。IG有個帳 @thejackjai 已經post左好多佢嘅仆街野。"},{"pid":"9d56749d6304a19e85e94a8677986cba8b3bdb45","tid":1954770,"uid":122234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T05:07:37.000Z","msg":"推！！"},{"pid":"642b8b8f5e869d423691130b332a3a069be436b3","tid":1954770,"uid":122234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T05:08:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"26918730c297ed1a254039849bc6d1776a297fea","tid":1954770,"uid":69107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T05:09:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3747b322c2bc62bdecf8ca88fa1ad3b2e5bfba4","tid":1954770,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T05:12:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87592a4b1e7d9cf5a94d6ba97a8317dbf9a7f2a0","tid":1954770,"uid":212473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T05:13:46.000Z","msg":"一年前已經聽過"},{"pid":"49ce6738cc4312b2ce2